	<dl>
	<dt>Because I'm a tax exile</dt>
	<dd><p>I live in Monaco to avoid paying any tax whatsover to support the schools and hospitals in the UK which brought me into this world. I consequently feel such profound guilt that I have decided it would be wrong of me to vote at the next general election. </p>
	<small>
	written 14th Jan 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/11">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=11">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

